# crontab: periodic tasks
#
# Modules self-register their own default entries on first boot via
# cronDefault() (see duckdns.cpp, acme.cpp, log.cpp). Edit or remove lines
# freely — modules respect user edits across reboots and only re-add when
# their s.<mod>.version key is bumped.
#
# flags:
#
#   -   none
#   A   When already awake, not on brief deepsleep wakeup
#   N   When STA connected to upstream network (AP-only does not count)
#
# min  hour dom  mon  dow  flag command

